sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Utilisateur (navigateur)
    participant SRV1 as SRV-1 - Serveur applicatif (Flask, port 5000)
    participant SRV2 as SRV-2 - Serveur de base de données (PostgreSQL)

    U->>SRV1: GET http://lechatdethomas.local/ (port 80)
    SRV1->>SRV2: SELECT messages ORDER BY date_post DESC
    SRV2-->>SRV1: liste des messages
    SRV1-->>U: page HTML (index.html rendu)

    U->>SRV1: POST /poster (pseudo, contenu)
    SRV1->>SRV1: validation (pseudo et contenu non vides)
    alt champs valides
        SRV1->>SRV2: INSERT INTO message (pseudo, contenu, date_post)
        SRV2-->>SRV1: OK
    else champ(s) manquant(s)
        SRV1->>SRV1: aucune écriture
    end
    SRV1-->>U: redirect 302 vers
